update.name: IngressNightmare-RCE-POC
update.description: PoC for CVE-2025-1974: Critical RCE in Ingress-NGINX (<v1.12.1) via unsafe config injection. Exploitable from the pod network without credentials, enabling code execution and potential cluster takeover. Fixed in v1.12.1 and v1.11.5. For research/education only.
